{"tid":100034,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"隔離屋個賓妹又播jw首小故事","createTime":"2017-01-29T16:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T18:17:02.000Z","uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f01a02ecc96d40dd50faeac7e0c8df835430e845","tid":100034,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:07:38.000Z","msg":"聖誕節果時已經係咁, 隔離屋係聖誕節去外國旅行, 剩番個賓賓看門口, 有日出街開門咁岩見到佢哋度門開著, 聽到首歌, 咁我就口多問左句：you love cantonese song? This one is good. 隻賓賓就話：my master is not here, they are out on vacation. 咁就每隔住一陣就聽到首歌不停repeat, 特別係夜晚12點之後, 到27號左右就停<br />\n<br />\n到尋日年初一, 隔離又開始loop jw首小故事, 又係夜晚, 而且loop得幾密吓, 本來都覺得無乜嘢, 當有d娛樂咁有歌聽咁, 首歌又幾甜又易入腦, 聽多陣就發覺開始有少少催眠, 著迷feel, 岩岩又開始播&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"5c77762fb1d54674d1401391ae0cbce05354c8f8","tid":100034,"uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:26:34.000Z","msg":"有潛力做潮文寫晒全部節日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a5a5ed46e45a48e7670d778ad28be0bc716b0e","tid":100034,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:17:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有潛力做潮文寫晒全部節日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}